Text:
This movie is a remake of "Evil Dead" from the 80s.  I like this one a little better. :) 

A=10
V=10

It has Korean subtitles hard coded, so you will need to look past that. It's easy though because the Korean words are so small and white so they blend in and you hardly notice they're even there. :) Thanks TvTeam for another great, high quality, quick download.
